        <mxCell id="wjzWpvQ6WlecAIslC05h-1" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;section m-0 p-0 img-text  d-block&quot; data-for=&quot;cmlist&quot; id=&quot;yui_3_18_1_1_1777346085967_219&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0.2em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Barlow, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15.2px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-right: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px !important; display: block !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;activity label modtype_label  hasinfo&quot; id=&quot;module-168436&quot; data-for=&quot;cmitem&quot; data-id=&quot;168436&quot; data-indexed=&quot;true&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25rem 0px 5px; padding: 0px; line-height: inherit; list-style: none; border-top: 1px solid rgb(222, 226, 230); clear: both; background: inherit; color: inherit; text-shadow: none; white-space: normal; display: block; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;activity-item focus-control&quot; data-activityname=&quot;EJERCICIO 8&quot; data-region=&quot;activity-card&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 1rem; border: 0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;activity-grid noname-grid&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: grid; align-items: center; grid-template-columns: min-content 1fr min-content min-content; grid-template-rows: 1fr repeat(5, min-content); grid-template-areas: &amp;quot;visibility groupmode completion actions&amp;quot; &amp;quot;altcontent altcontent altcontent altcontent&amp;quot; &amp;quot;afterlink afterlink afterlink afterlink&amp;quot; &amp;quot;availability availability availability availability&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;activity-altcontent text-break&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25rem 0px 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; word-break: break-word !important; grid-area: altcontent;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;no-overflow&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: auto; width: 1885.64px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;no-overflow&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: auto; width: 1885.64px;&quot;&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.5rem; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 1.6625rem; font-family: Roboto;&quot;&gt;EJERCICIO 8&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;“Se necesita una base de datos de los diferentes modelos de autos del mercado. Por cada modelo se desea saber la marca, nombre y precio actual.&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: inherit; color: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;También se requiere conocer el motor que posee, el cual tiene su nombre propio, cilindrada, potencia y marca (que no tiene por qué ser igual a la del auto). Las marcas se encuentran clasificadas según su nacionalidad. Cada modelo se compone además de diferentes accesorios y, de acuerdo al modelo, el accesorio puede estar incluido o ser opcional en la compra (ej: alarma). Cada accesorio tiene su propio código”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;activity label modtype_label  hasinfo&quot; id=&quot;module-198933&quot; data-for=&quot;cmitem&quot; data-id=&quot;198933&quot; data-indexed=&quot;true&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25rem 0px 5px; padding: 0px; line-height: inherit; list-style: none; border-top: 1px solid rgb(222, 226, 230); clear: both; background: inherit; color: inherit; text-shadow: none; white-space: normal; display: block; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;activity-item focus-control activityinline&quot; data-activityname=&quot;ej7&quot; data-region=&quot;activity-card&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75rem 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;activity-grid noname-grid&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: grid; align-items: center; grid-template-columns: min-content 1fr min-content min-content; grid-template-rows: 1fr repeat(5, min-content); grid-template-areas: &amp;quot;visibility groupmode completion actions&amp;quot; &amp;quot;altcontent altcontent altcontent altcontent&amp;quot; &amp;quot;afterlink afterlink afterlink afterlink&amp;quot; &amp;quot;availability availability availability availability&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;activity-altcontent text-break&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25rem 0px 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; word-break: break-word !important; grid-area: altcontent;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;no-overflow&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: auto; width: 1917.64px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;no-overflow&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: auto; width: 1917.64px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br class=&quot;Apple-interchange-newline&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
